product.bullet_points:
• ❤Dessert Table Display Set: You will receive 9 pieces cake stands, including 1 x 3-tier cake trays, 2 x rectangular cake trays, 3 x variety of sizes cake stands with base, 2 x small cupcake stand with base, and 1 x heart-shape tray. It is sufficient for daily use or festive hospitality.
• ❤Exquisite Workmanship: The cupcake stand adopted exquisite hollow design, which looks very artistic. Our cake stands are made of high quality & sturdy metal, direct contact with food is very safe. The top tray is smooth, bright and flat without scratches.
• ❤Easy to Assemble: It is easy to install the dessert holder, just connect the top tray and the base. Then you can use it for your exquisite desserts display. You can tear down the tiers for easy storage. When cleaning the stand, simply wipe the surface with a damp cloth.
• ❤ Multiple Usage: The serving tray set allows you to serve more and different kinds of treats. Great for appetizers, cheese displays, fresh veggies, cookies, cakes, macaron, doughnut, fruit, snacks, cupcakes, fruit, desserts, and so much more.
• ❤ Wide Application: It is suitable for most events and parties such as tea parties, baby shower, graduation, wedding, Christmas, Thanksgiving, or home decor. These plates will make your table look cleaner and save space, and will definitely receive a lot of praise from guests.
